Feature: GitHubに対するUI操作
  https://intuit.github.io/karate/karate-core/

Background:
  * configure driver = { type: 'chrome' }
  # * configure driver = { type: 'chromedriver' }
  # * configure driver = { type: 'geckodriver' }
  # * configure driver = { type: 'safaridriver' }
